http://www.sohu.com/a/416475505_157635	32948
<p><img src="http://p2.itc.cn/q_70/images03/20200904/e18b7d69001d4711bc71cd198017b267.jpeg" /></p>
<p><span>岳云鹏发出与魏大勋合影</span></p>
